WEBVTT

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:35.376
They said the stores who sold the guns
and the owners who bought them

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:38.120
were responsible
should anything bad happen.

00:08:39.559 --> 00:08:42.096
In response to this
and many other lawsuits,

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:46.120
the NRA lobbied
for the passage of the PLCAA,

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:50.976
the Protection of Lawful
Commerce in Arms Act.

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:56.336
The PLCAA passed
with bipartisan support in 2005

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:58.896
and entrusts gun manufacturers

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:01.456
to design guns safely,